# Revenue Streams

## 1. Funding Origination Fee

Charged to businesses when funding is released.

Example:

Funding Amount:
₱20,000

Origination Fee:
5%

Revenue:
₱1,000

---

## 2. Platform Management Fee

Percentage deducted from investment returns.

Example:

Investor Profit:
₱1,000

Platform Fee:
15%

Vestara Revenue:
₱150

---

## 3. Withdrawal Processing Fee

Example:

| Withdrawal    | Fee |
| ------------- | --- |
| ₱100–₱999     | ₱10 |
| ₱1,000–₱4,999 | ₱20 |
| ₱5,000+       | ₱50 |

