### Important Regulatory Note

The financial projections above assume Vestara can legally operate the proposed funding model. Before accepting public funds or offering returns, obtain legal advice regarding requirements from the Philippine financial regulatory framework, including potential oversight by the Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas, Securities and Exchange Commission, and Anti-Money Laundering Council. This should be part of the initial funding budget.
